    "body": "The tx is a `type 2` transaction, which means the _effective_ gas price depends on the block -- it cannot be determined given only the transaction. \r\nHere's an example of how we pick it up in another place in the code (ethapi/api.go): \r\n```\r\n\t\tgasPrice := new(big.Int).Add(header.BaseFee, tx.EffectiveGasTipValue(header.BaseFee))\r\n```\r\n",
